International Finance Corporation

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


International Finance Corporation


IFC headquarters building, designed by architect Michael Graves




IFC logo



Formation
July 20, 1956


Type
Development finance institution


Legal status
